ights and humanitarian law from Universit&eacute; de Paris II, Panth&eacute;on&ndash;Assas in France, and a certificate in international migration studies from Georgetown University. She is a native Spanish speaker and is fluent in English, Portuguese, and French.\u003C/p>","analia@riossocialjustice.org",[32,53,76,100,120,143,165],{"id":33,"name":34,"slug":35,"role":36,"photo":37,"outline":51},"OtPTU6GHQhS5GfVPnYlpnw","Silvia Serrano-Guzmán","silvia-serrano-guzman","Co-Executive Director",{"id":38,"alt":11,"title":11,"focalPoint":39,"width":40,"height":40,"thumbnail":41,"small":42,"medium":43,"responsiveImage":44,"video":11},"KStwRHp-R_efZJrfuprKIA",{"x":13,"y":13},400,"/assets/datocms/1763550764-headshot-9-jpg.avif?auto=format&fit=max&h=600&q=85&w=600","/assets/datocms/1763550764-headshot-9-jpg.avif?auto=format&fit=max&h=1000&q=85&w=1000","/assets/datocms/1763550764-headshot-9-jpg.avif?auto=format&fit=max&h=1500&q=85&w=1500",{"srcSet":45,"webpSrcSet":21,"sizes":46,"src":47,"width":40,"height":40,"aspectRatio":48,"alt":11,"title":11,"base64":49,"bgColor":50},"/assets/datocms/1763550764-headshot-9-jpg.avif?auto=format&dpr=0.25&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 100w,/assets/datocms/1763550764-headshot-9-jpg.avif?auto=format&dpr=0.5&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 200w,/assets/datocms/1763550764-headshot-9-jpg.avif?auto=format&dpr=0.75&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 300w,/assets/datocms/1763550764-headshot-9-jpg.avif?auto=format&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440 400w","(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px","/assets/datocms/1763550764-headshot-9-jpg.avif?auto=format&fit=max&h=2440&q=85&w=2440",1,"data:image/jpeg;base64,","#b9825f",{"hex":52},"#115767",{"id":54,"name":55,"slug":56,"role":36,"photo":57,"outline":74},"PRyoLHIvTdS-35tv-G8jUA","Oscar Cabrera","oscar-cabrera",{"id":58,"alt":11,"title":11,"focalPoint":59,"width":62,"height":63,"thumbnail":64,"small":65,"medium":66,"responsiveImage":67,"video":11},"TkB4dklGSx25yEWY4DmenQ",{"x":60,"y":61},0.45,0.28,480,509,"/assets/datocms/1764087557-oac_p